## 2026-05-26

### Add Mandatory keys to MP2RAGE json
    RepetitionTimeExcitation: required
    RepetitionTimePreparation: required
    NumberShots: required

```bash
bids_dir="/data_/mica3/BIDS_PNI/rawdata"
for subses in sub*/ses*; do
    sub=$(echo "$subses" | cut -d'/' -f1)
    ses=$(echo "$subses" | cut -d'/' -f2)
    mp2rage_keys.py -sub ${sub/sub-/} -ses ${ses/ses-} -bids ${bids_dir}
done
```

